title: Does the pixel 3a Titan chip work with a FIDO key that one can buy in Spain?
content:
Does the pixel 3a work with a FIDO key that I could buy in Spain?
The key that google offers to work with the Titan chip is only available in the USA.
I would like to buy a key in Spain to make use of the TITAN chip on the 3a.
Even if the Titan chip is not working in Spain could I use a FIDO chip?
Jeff
